		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You command a creature to submit to your power, and as you worm your way into they mind, you bend a small piece of iron. As you do, your target feels as if they are unable to move more than slightly, as if chained by invisible chains.</em></p><p><strong>[[/save wis]]{Wisdom Save}</strong></p><ul><li aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"auto\"><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target is &amp;reference[Restrained]. Target rolls again at end of their turns, ending effect on success.</p></li><li aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"auto\"><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li></ul><p>* <strong>Upcasting:</strong> Target one additional creature for each spell level above 2nd.</p>",
